{"tid":1431790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大乜撚台","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:21:58.000Z","uid":264369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d84adbff58ec585616d8926b6c4147a3498d175e","tid":1431790,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"大台唔係一個台<br />\n大台係指有權操控群眾發言權背後的力量<br />\n力量可以係大會主辦人，可以係傳統習慣上某Ｄ岡位，可以係KOL，...<br />\n大台只係個形象化左嘅代名詞<br />\n冇大台，係權力歸予群眾<br />\n冇<span style=\"color: red;\">平台</span>，大家卻永遠只係一盤散沙<br />\n<br />\n大家要努力 work out 的，係如何令平台唔會變成大台<br />\n而唔係盲目地馮台必反<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會係一個好開始，不過大家仍要小心監察<br />\n千里之行始於足下，唔踏出第一步你就永遠只會原地踏步<br />\n冇大台－始於香港，始於你地<br />\n大家係要小心揍大佢<br />\n唔係合埋眼揪佢"},{"pid":"ee7d0b6f24977658e69de2c7a290455873a8c58f","tid":1431790,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HI三毛</span>"},{"pid":"f99e1d2dbca101ac3548de759c9506f55347408e","tid":1431790,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7d0b6f24977658e69de2c7a290455873a8c58f","tid":1431790,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HI三毛</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"Hi一毛"},{"pid":"df7a08e6f14e85cde778ad4b602c12530293ec26","tid":1431790,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}